'''美國網球協會比莉·珍·金網球中心'''（USTA Billie Jean King National Tennis Center）是[[美國網球公開賽|美國網球公開賽]]的主場館，位於[[法拉盛草原可樂娜公園|法拉盛草原可樂娜公園]]。世界最大的網球專用球場[[亞瑟·艾許球場|亞瑟·艾許球場]]也位於美國網球協會比莉·珍·金網球中心。美國網球協會比莉·珍·金網球中心修建於1978年<ref name=History>[http://www.usta.com/About-USTA/National-Tennis-Center/Information/14189_History_of_the_USTA_Billie_Jean_King_National_Tennis_Center History of the USTA Billie Jean King National Tennis Center] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110101054545/http://www.usta.com/About-USTA/National-Tennis-Center/Information/14189_History_of_the_USTA_Billie_Jean_King_National_Tennis_Center/ |date=2011-01-01 }}. National Tennis Center official webpage. USTA official website. Retrieved 2011-02-15.</ref>，2008年改為現名<ref name=AboutTheUSTABillieJeanKingNational>[http://www.usta.com/About-USTA/National-Tennis-Center/Information/14191_USTA_Billie_Jean_King_National_Tennis_Center_Information About The USTA Billie Jean King National Tennis Center] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110101054752/http://www.usta.com/About-USTA/National-Tennis-Center/Information/14191_USTA_Billie_Jean_King_National_Tennis_Center_Information/ |date=2011-01-01 }}. National Tennis Center official webpage. USTA official website. Retrieved 2011-02-15.</ref>。

